oai_dc:dc.dc:description: One of the major issues new graduates face is simply earning the confidence of their clients. Being able to conduct a necropsy efficiently and effectively is 1 way to gain the client's confidence. This article includes necropsy tips and techniques the author has developed over 25 years of beef cattle practice.
